00 EVOL

Congratulations! You have found the special token!

With purchase of this token, the holder can request a custom EVOL to their specification. The Deal lasts for the length of the tokens life (or KidEights, which ever burns first)

Token can be traded and the offer still stands to the new owner. (The Token must be purchased, gifting/trading will void the agreement)

Will you burn the token and have the only custom EVOL, or choose to share the wealth? You Decide!
